{"content": "/* Modern design using a clean layout with main color orange */

/* Reset default browser styles */
* {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #333;
  background-color: #f4f4f4;
  padding: 20px;
}

header {
  background-color: #ff6600; /* Main color: orange */
  color: #fff;
  padding: 20px 0;
  text-align: center;
}

header h1 {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  font-size: 2.5rem;
}

nav ul {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
}

nav ul li {
  margin: 0 15px;
}

nav ul li a {
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
}

nav ul li a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

main {
  margin: 20px auto;
  max-width: 1000px;
  background: #fff;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

main h2 {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: #ff6600;
  font-size: 2rem;
}

main h3 {
  margin-top: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  color: #ff6600;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}

section p, section ul {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  font-size: 1rem;
}

section ul li {
  margin-left: 20px;
  list-style-type: disc;
}

footer {
  text-align: center;
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 10px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #777;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
  nav ul {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  nav ul li {
    margin: 10px 0;
  }
}
